# Netbox QR Code Plugin

A [NetBox] plugin used to generate QR codes for objects: Device, Module,
Cable, Powerfeed, Powerpanel, Location 

This plugin depends on [qrcode] and [Pillow] python library

[Downloads]
[Downloads]
[Downloads]

